/F1 20 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 738.00 Tm
(Formal RL Length Generalization) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 696.00 Tm
(A technical handbook for the `formal_rl_length_generalization` implementation.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 668.00 Tm
(Date: June 4, 2026) Tj
/F1 14 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 626.00 Tm
(Preface) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 584.00 Tm
(This handbook explains the theory and implementation behind the) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 570.00 Tm
(`formal_rl_length_generalization` project. The project studies whether small autoregressive) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 556.00 Tm
(Transformer policies can learn length-generalizing algorithms for formal-language) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 542.00 Tm
(recognition when trained with PPO or GRPO and oracle process rewards.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 514.00 Tm
(The core experimental question is whether dense rewards on intermediate reasoning states) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 500.00 Tm
(help a model learn an algorithm, rather than merely fitting short training examples.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 472.00 Tm
(The codebase implements four task families:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 444.00 Tm
(- parity) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 430.00 Tm
(- modular counting with `k = 3` and `k = 5`) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 416.00 Tm
(- `a*b*`) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 402.00 Tm
(- `a^n b^n`) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 374.00 Tm
(It supports seven training regimes:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 346.00 Tm
(- supervised CoT baseline) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 332.00 Tm
(- PPO terminal-only reward) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 318.00 Tm
(- PPO oracle process reward) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 304.00 Tm
(- PPO process plus terminal reward) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 290.00 Tm
(- GRPO terminal-only reward) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 276.00 Tm
(- GRPO oracle process reward) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 262.00 Tm
(- GRPO process plus terminal reward) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 234.00 Tm
(Training lengths are restricted to:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 206.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 192.00 Tm
(n = 1, 2, ..., 40) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 178.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 150.00 Tm
(OOD evaluation lengths are:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 122.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 108.00 Tm
(41-80) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 94.00 Tm
(81-160) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 80.00 Tm
(161-320) Tj
