/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 724.00 Tm
(The model receives a prompt:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 696.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 682.00 Tm
(TASK <task_name> INPUT x_1 x_2 ... x_n TRACE) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 668.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 640.00 Tm
(and must generate:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 612.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 598.00 Tm
(s_1 s_2 ... s_n FINAL y_final) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 584.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 556.00 Tm
(For `a^n b^n`, the trace contains two tokens per timestep:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 528.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 514.00 Tm
(phase_t BAL_balance_t) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 500.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 472.00 Tm
(so the target is:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 444.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 430.00 Tm
(phase_1 BAL_b1 phase_2 BAL_b2 ... phase_n BAL_bn FINAL accept/reject) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 416.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 388.00 Tm
(The model is therefore trained not only to classify a string, but also to emit an explicit) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 374.00 Tm
(computation trace.) Tj
/F1 14 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 332.00 Tm
(3. Reward Decomposition) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 290.00 Tm
(All RL algorithms use two basic reward components.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 262.00 Tm
(The process reward measures correctness of the intermediate trace:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 234.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 220.00 Tm
(R_process = average intermediate-state correctness) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 206.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 178.00 Tm
(The terminal reward measures correctness of the final answer:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 150.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 136.00 Tm
(R_terminal = 1[predicted final answer is correct]) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 122.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 94.00 Tm
(The combined reward mode is:) Tj
/F1 9 Tf
1 0 0 1 478 30 Tm
(Page 3 of 20) Tj
ET
