/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 738.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 724.00 Tm
(R_terminal = 1[hat_accept = accept]) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 710.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 682.00 Tm
(This is also regular, but it requires a cyclic state machine with `k` states.) Tj
/F1 14 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 640.00 Tm
(6. Task 3: a*b*) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 598.00 Tm
(The language `a*b*` contains strings with zero or more `a`s followed by zero or more `b`s.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 584.00 Tm
(Once `b` appears, no `a` may appear afterward.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 556.00 Tm
(The DFA states are:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 528.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 514.00 Tm
(S0 = still reading a's) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 500.00 Tm
(S1 = reading b's) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 486.00 Tm
(S2 = dead/invalid) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 472.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 444.00 Tm
(The transition function is:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 416.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 402.00 Tm
(delta\(S0, a\) = S0) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 388.00 Tm
(delta\(S0, b\) = S1) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 374.00 Tm
(delta\(S1, b\) = S1) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 360.00 Tm
(delta\(S1, a\) = S2) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 346.00 Tm
(delta\(S2, a\) = S2) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 332.00 Tm
(delta\(S2, b\) = S2) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 318.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 290.00 Tm
(The accept condition is:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 262.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 248.00 Tm
(accept iff s_n in {S0, S1}) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 234.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 206.00 Tm
(The process reward is:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 178.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 164.00 Tm
(R_process = \(1/n\) sum_{t=1}^n 1[hat_s_t = s_t]) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 150.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 122.00 Tm
(The terminal reward is:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 94.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 80.00 Tm
(R_terminal = 1[hat_accept = accept]) Tj
