BT
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 738.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 710.00 Tm
(This task tests phase tracking and invalid-state detection.) Tj
/F1 14 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 668.00 Tm
(7. Task 4: a^n b^n) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 626.00 Tm
(The language `a^n b^n` is context-free. A valid string has a block of `a`s followed by an) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 612.00 Tm
(equally long block of `b`s.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 584.00 Tm
(The implementation uses a canonical state with two components:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 556.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 542.00 Tm
(phase_t in {A_PHASE, B_PHASE, DEAD}) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 528.00 Tm
(balance_t = count_a_t - count_b_t) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 514.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 486.00 Tm
(Counts are:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 458.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 444.00 Tm
(count_a_t = number of a's seen up to time t) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 430.00 Tm
(count_b_t = number of b's seen up to time t) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 416.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 388.00 Tm
(The balance is:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 360.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 346.00 Tm
(balance_t = count_a_t - count_b_t) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 332.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 304.00 Tm
(The phase tracks whether the sequence is still in the `a` block, has entered the `b` block,) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 290.00 Tm
(or has become invalid.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 262.00 Tm
(The model emits:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 234.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 220.00 Tm
(phase_t BAL_balance_t) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 206.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 178.00 Tm
(at every timestep.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 150.00 Tm
(The phase reward is:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 122.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 108.00 Tm
(R_phase\(t\) = 1[hat_phase_t = phase_t]) Tj
