/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 514.00 Tm
(The probability ratio is:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 486.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 472.00 Tm
(rho_t\(theta\)) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 458.00 Tm
(= pi_theta\(a_t | s_t\) / pi_theta_old\(a_t | s_t\)) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 444.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 416.00 Tm
(Using log probabilities:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 388.00 Tm
