/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 248.00 Tm
(GRPO samples multiple completions for the same prompt.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 220.00 Tm
(For prompt `q_i`, sample:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 192.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 178.00 Tm
(a_i,1, a_i,2, ..., a_i,K) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 164.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 136.00 Tm
(Each completion receives reward:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 108.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 94.00 Tm
(R_i,k) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 80.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 9 Tf
1 0 0 1 478 30 Tm
(Page 14 of 20) Tj
