29 0 obj
<< /Type /Page /Parent 42 0 R /MediaBox [0 0 612 792] /Resources << /Font << /F1 1 0 R >> >> /Contents 28 0 R >>
endobj
30 0 obj
<< /Length 1928 >>
stream
BT
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 724.00 Tm
(The group mean is:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 696.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 682.00 Tm
(mu_i = \(1/K\) sum_{k=1}^K R_i,k) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 668.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 640.00 Tm
(The group standard deviation is:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 612.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 598.00 Tm
(sigma_i = sqrt\(\(1/K\) sum_{k=1}^K \(R_i,k - mu_i\)^2\)) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 584.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 556.00 Tm
(The group-relative advantage is:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 528.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 514.00 Tm
(A_i,k = \(R_i,k - mu_i\) / \(sigma_i + epsilon\)) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 500.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 472.00 Tm
(The clipped GRPO loss is PPO-like:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 444.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 430.00 Tm
(L_GRPO_policy) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 416.00 Tm
(= -mean_{i,k,t} min\(rho_i,k,t A_i,k,) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 402.00 Tm
(clip\(rho_i,k,t, 1-epsilon, 1+epsilon\) A_i,k\)) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 388.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 360.00 Tm
(GRPO also uses entropy regularization:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 332.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 318.00 Tm
(L_GRPO = L_GRPO_policy - c_H H) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 304.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 276.00 Tm
(There is no value loss in GRPO:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 248.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 234.00 Tm
(L_value is absent) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 220.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 192.00 Tm
(This is the key difference:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 164.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 150.00 Tm
(PPO baseline  = learned value model) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 136.00 Tm
(GRPO baseline = relative performance among samples for the same prompt) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 122.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 9 Tf
1 0 0 1 478 30 Tm
(Page 15 of 20) Tj
ET
