BT
/F1 14 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 724.00 Tm
(15. Why Process Rewards Help) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 682.00 Tm
(Terminal-only reward asks:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 654.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 640.00 Tm
(Was the final answer correct?) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 626.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 598.00 Tm
(Process reward asks:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 570.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 556.00 Tm
(Was the computation correct at each prefix?) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 542.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 514.00 Tm
(For parity, the process reward checks whether the model updates the parity bit after every) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 500.00 Tm
(input bit.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 472.00 Tm
(For modular counting, it checks the residue class after every input.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 444.00 Tm
(For `a*b*`, it checks the DFA state.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 416.00 Tm
(For `a^n b^n`, it checks phase and balance.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 388.00 Tm
(This is a much richer learning signal. It encourages the model to implement the recurrence:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 360.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 346.00 Tm
(s_t = f\(s_{t-1}, x_t\)) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 332.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 304.00 Tm
(instead of only learning a shortcut to the final label.) Tj
/F1 14 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 262.00 Tm
(16. Length Generalization) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 220.00 Tm
(The train set only contains lengths up to 40. A non-algorithmic model can exploit this. It) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 206.00 Tm
(may memorize short templates or learn length-specific heuristics.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 178.00 Tm
(Length generalization requires the learned transition rule to remain valid for longer) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 164.00 Tm
(sequences:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 136.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 122.00 Tm
(s_t = f\(s_{t-1}, x_t\)) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 108.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 80.00 Tm
(For parity:) Tj
/F1 9 Tf
1 0 0 1 478 30 Tm
(Page 16 of 20) Tj
ET
endstream
