BT
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 724.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 710.00 Tm
(f\(p, x\) = p XOR x) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 696.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 668.00 Tm
(For modular counting:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 640.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 626.00 Tm
(f\(c, x\) = \(c + x\) mod k) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 612.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 584.00 Tm
(For `a*b*`, `f` is the DFA transition function.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 556.00 Tm
(For `a^n b^n`, `f` updates phase and balance.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 528.00 Tm
(The central bet of the project is that rewarding the intermediate state makes this) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 514.00 Tm
(transition rule easier to learn.) Tj
/F1 14 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 472.00 Tm
(17. Evaluation Metrics) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 430.00 Tm
(The implementation reports three main metrics.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 402.00 Tm
(Process score:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 374.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 360.00 Tm
(mean R_process) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 346.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 318.00 Tm
(Terminal score:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 290.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 276.00 Tm
(mean R_terminal) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 262.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 234.00 Tm
(Exact score:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 206.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 192.00 Tm
(1[generated target prefix exactly equals oracle target]) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 178.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 150.00 Tm
(Exact score is strict. A model can have useful process behavior but fail exact match because) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 136.00 Tm
(of formatting mistakes. Terminal score is useful for language recognition, while process) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 122.00 Tm
(score is useful for diagnosing whether the model learned the intended computation.) Tj
/F1 9 Tf
1 0 0 1 478 30 Tm
(Page 17 of 20) Tj
