/F1 14 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 724.00 Tm
(18. Implementation Map) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 682.00 Tm
(The major files are:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 654.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 640.00 Tm
(tasks.py       task generators, oracle traces, rewards) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 626.00 Tm
(tokenizer.py   fixed symbolic tokenizer) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 612.00 Tm
(model.py       causal Transformer policy and value model) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 598.00 Tm
(train.py       SFT/PPO/GRPO training entrypoint) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 584.00 Tm
(rl.py          rollout collection and PPO/GRPO updates) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 570.00 Tm
(evaluate.py    length-bucket evaluation utilities) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 556.00 Tm
(eval.py        checkpoint evaluation CLI) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 542.00 Tm
(configs/       example experiment configs) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 528.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 500.00 Tm
(The implementation is intentionally compact so that experiments can be modified quickly.) Tj
/F1 14 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 458.00 Tm
(19. Important Limitations) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 416.00 Tm
(The current codebase is a research scaffold, not a full production RLHF implementation.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 388.00 Tm
(Important limitations:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 360.00 Tm
(- PPO broadcasts one sequence-level reward to all generated tokens.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 346.00 Tm
(- The process reward is computed after generation rather than inserted as per-token reward) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 332.00 Tm
(  during rollout.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 318.00 Tm
(- PPO does not yet implement full reward-to-go or GAE.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 304.00 Tm
(- There is no KL penalty against a frozen reference model.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 290.00 Tm
(- Evaluation up to length 500 can be slow on CPU.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 276.00 Tm
(- The generation format is strict; malformed traces may receive poor reward even when) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 262.00 Tm
(  partially meaningful.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 234.00 Tm
(These limitations are useful future improvement points.) Tj
/F1 14 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 192.00 Tm
(20. Natural Next Extensions) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 150.00 Tm
(A stronger PPO implementation would use token-aligned process reward:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 122.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 108.00 Tm
(r_t = oracle reward for the generated state token at time t) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 94.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 9 Tf
1 0 0 1 478 30 Tm
(Page 18 of 20) Tj
ET
endstream
