BT
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 738.00 Tm
(Then reward-to-go would be:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 710.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 696.00 Tm
(G_t = sum_{u=t}^T gamma^\(u-t\) r_u) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 682.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 654.00 Tm
(GAE would use:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 626.00 Tm
