/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 528.00 Tm
(A_t^GAE = sum_l \(gamma lambda\)^l delta_{t+l}) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 514.00 Tm
(```) Tj
