1 0 0 1 54 486.00 Tm
(Other extensions:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 458.00 Tm
(- frozen reference policy and KL penalty) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 444.00 Tm
(- deterministic decoding for evaluation) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 430.00 Tm
(- curriculum schedules within `n <= 40`) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 416.00 Tm
(- per-length plots instead of only bucket averages) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 402.00 Tm
(- multiple seeds and confidence intervals) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 388.00 Tm
(- recurrent or stack-augmented baselines) Tj
/F1 14 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 346.00 Tm
(21. How to Interpret Results) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 304.00 Tm
(Strong evidence for algorithmic learning would be:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 276.00 Tm
(- high training process accuracy) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 262.00 Tm
(- high training terminal accuracy) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 248.00 Tm
(- high OOD process accuracy) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 234.00 Tm
(- high OOD terminal accuracy) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 220.00 Tm
(- graceful degradation as length increases) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 206.00 Tm
(- process-reward PPO/GRPO outperforming terminal-only PPO/GRPO) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 178.00 Tm
