/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 122.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 94.00 Tm
(That suggests memorization or short-length heuristics.) Tj
/F1 9 Tf
1 0 0 1 478 30 Tm
