/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 738.00 Tm
(Another interesting result is:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 710.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 696.00 Tm
(high process accuracy but low terminal accuracy) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 682.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 654.00 Tm
(That may indicate formatting or final-token problems rather than a failure to learn the) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 640.00 Tm
(underlying state transition.) Tj
/F1 14 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 598.00 Tm
(22. Summary) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 556.00 Tm
(The project turns formal-language recognition into autoregressive trace generation. The) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 542.00 Tm
(Transformer policy generates symbolic computation traces. The oracle rewards either the) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 528.00 Tm
(final answer, the intermediate computation, or both.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 500.00 Tm
(PPO uses a learned value baseline and clipped policy updates. GRPO uses multiple completions) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 486.00 Tm
(for the same prompt and group-relative advantage normalization.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 458.00 Tm
(The central scientific claim being tested is:) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 430.00 Tm
(```text) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 416.00 Tm
(If the model learns the true state-transition rule, it should generalize) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 402.00 Tm
(beyond the lengths it saw during training.) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 388.00 Tm
(```) Tj
/F1 10.5 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 360.00 Tm
(Process rewards are designed to make learning that rule easier.) Tj
/F1 9 Tf
1 0 0 1 478 30 Tm
(Page 20 of 20) Tj
ET
endstream
